  - elementId: flow2-badge
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [800, 232, 90, 20]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#7C3AED"
  - elementId: flow2-badge-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [800, 232, 90, 20]
    content:
      fontSize: 10
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>FLOW AUTH</strong></p>
  - elementId: flow2-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [800, 256, 420, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>Navigateur → <strong>Kimi OAuth</strong> → callback /api/auth/callback → JWT genere + cookie session → tRPC context extrait le role utilisateur.</p>

