    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$light"}
  - elementId: rel1-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 515, 4, 115]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"
  - elementId: rel1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [76, 520, 340, 20]
    content:
      fontSize: 13
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>React ↔ tRPC Client</strong></p>
  - elementId: rel1-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [76, 542, 340, 80]
    content:
      fontSize: 11
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>Les hooks React appellent les procedures tRPC comme des <strong>fonctions TypeScript locales</strong>. Le client gere automatiquement le cache, le dedup, le retry et l'invalidation des requêtes.</p>

  - elementId: rel2-box
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [455, 515, 370, 115]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$white"
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$light"}
  - elementId: rel2-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [455, 515, 4, 115]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#7C3AED"
  - elementId: rel2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [471, 520, 340, 20]
    content:
      fontSize: 13
      color: "#7C3AED"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Router ↔ RBAC ↔ Drizzle</strong></p>
  - elementId: rel2-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [471, 542, 340, 80]
    content:
      fontSize: 11
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>Chaque requête passe par la <strong>chaine middleware</strong> : authentification JWT → extraction du role → verification projectMembers → execution Drizzle. Le tout est <strong>type-safe de bout en bout</strong>.</p>

  - elementId: rel3-box
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [850, 515, 370, 115]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$white"
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$light"}
  - elementId: rel3-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [850, 515, 4, 115]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#F59E0B"
  - elementId: rel3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [866, 520, 340, 20]
    content:
      fontSize: 13
      color: "#F59E0B"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Firebase ↔ MySQL (complementarite)</strong></p>
  - elementId: rel3-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [866, 542, 340, 80]
    content:
      fontSize: 11
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>MySQL = <strong>source de verite</strong> pour les donnees metier. Firebase = <strong>couche de sync</strong> pour l'acces multi-appareils. Les deux sont independants — Firebase peut etre desactive sans impact.</p>

  # ===== FOOTER =====
  - elementId: bottom-line-footer
